@host = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = REPLACE_WITH_ADMIN_BEARER_TOKEN
@ts = {{$timestamp}}
@concertTitle = Admin-Concert-{{ts}}
@artistName = Admin-Artist-{{ts}}
@agencyName = Admin-Agency-{{ts}}

### 1) [Admin] 콘서트 생성
POST {{host}}/api/admin/concerts
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "{{concertTitle}}",
  "artistName": "{{artistName}}",
  "artistDisplayName": "{{artistName}}",
  "artistGenre": "K-POP",
  "artistDebutDate": "2022-07-22",
  "agencyName": "{{agencyName}}",
  "agencyCountryCode": "KR",
  "agencyHomepageUrl": "https://example.com/{{agencyName}}",
  "youtubeVideoUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U8A5sK5PRCI"
}
> {%
client.test("admin concert create success", function() {
  client.assert(response.status === 201, "expected 201");
});
if (response.body && response.body.id) {
  client.global.set("concertId", String(response.body.id));
}
%}

### 2) [Admin] 회차 생성(좌석/가격 포함)
POST {{host}}/api/admin/concerts/{{concertId}}/options
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "concertDate": "2026-06-01T18:00:00",
  "seatCount": 50,
  "ticketPriceAmount": 120000
}
> {%
client.test("admin option create success", function() {
  client.assert(response.status === 201, "expected 201");
});
if (response.body && response.body.id) {
  client.global.set("optionId", String(response.body.id));
}
%}

### 3) [Admin] 판매정책 생성/수정
PUT {{host}}/api/admin/concerts/{{concertId}}/sales-policy
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "presaleStartAt": "2026-05-01T12:00:00",
  "presaleEndAt": "2026-05-01T13:00:00",
  "presaleMinimumTier": "BASIC",
  "generalSaleStartAt": "2026-05-01T13:00:00",
  "maxReservationsPerUser": 2
}

### 4) [Admin] 썸네일 업로드 (multipart)
POST {{host}}/api/admin/concerts/{{concertId}}/thumbnail
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=AdminConcertBoundary

--AdminConcertBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="thumbnail.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./samples/thumbnail.jpg
--AdminConcertBoundary--

### 5) [Public] 목록/검색/옵션/좌석/썸네일 조회
GET {{host}}/api/concerts

###
GET {{host}}/api/concerts/search?keyword={{concertTitle}}&page=0&size=10&sort=id,desc

###
GET {{host}}/api/concerts/{{concertId}}/options

###
GET {{host}}/api/concerts/options/{{optionId}}/seats

###
GET {{host}}/api/concerts/{{concertId}}/thumbnail

### 6) [Admin] 회차 삭제 (선택)
DELETE {{host}}/api/admin/concerts/options/{{optionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7) [Admin] 콘서트 삭제 (선택)
DELETE {{host}}/api/admin/concerts/{{concertId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
